title: Spyder Auto Installation - 1998-2003 Dodge Durango, 96-00 Caravan/Voyager LED Tail Lights
description:
This video provides directions for how to install Spyder Auto's LED tail lights for the following models:
Dodge Caravan/Grand Caravan 96-00 / Dodge Durango 98-03 / Chrysler Town & Country 96-00 / Plymouth Voyager/Grand Voyager 96-00
These tail lights fit all of the above. This video focuses specifically on the Durango, however the method for installation is essentially the same.
